      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm looking at our latest audit for the Rotterdam hub and we have some weird discrepancies in the electronics section. Can you help me look at these numbers and suggest what might be causing the mismatch?\n\nItem ID | Expected Qty | Physical Count | Variance\nSKU-992-A | 1450 | 1442 | -8\nSKU-441-C | 890 | 889 | -1\nSKU-102-F | 320 | 314 | -6\nSKU-558-B | 2100 | 2098 | -2\n\nIt's mostly small amounts but it's happening every week.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
